# Data Engineer SQL DDL Cheat Sheet (PERFECTED) ✅

## 🔍 Navigation (No Switch Needed!)
```sql
SHOW DATABASES;           # All DBs
USE dev_db;               # Switch DB
SHOW TABLES;              # Current DB tables
DESC prod_db.users;       # Table schema ANYWHERE
```

## 🏗️ CREATE + 6 Constraints (INTERVIEW MUST!)
```sql
CREATE TABLE staff (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT,     # 1️⃣ PK + Auto-incr
    name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,             # 2️⃣ Mandatory
    age INT CHECK (age >= 18),             # 3️⃣ Validation
    email VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE,             # 4️⃣ No duplicates
    country VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'India',   # 5️⃣ Auto-fill
    dept_id INT,                           # 
    FOREIGN KEY (dept_id) REFERENCES depts(id)  # 6️⃣ Ref Integrity
);
```

## ⚙️ ALTER (Schema Evolution)
```sql
ALTER TABLE staff 
    ADD phone VARCHAR(15),           # ➕ Add col
    MODIFY name VARCHAR(100),        # 🔄 Change type
    RENAME COLUMN phone TO mobile,   # 📝 Rename
    DROP COLUMN mobile;              # ➖ Delete
```

## 🧹 Cleanup (Safe Order!)
```sql
RENAME TABLE staff TO employees;      # 📛 Rename table
TRUNCATE TABLE employees;             # 🗑️  Clear data (structure safe)
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS employees;       # ❌ Delete table
DROP DATABASE IF EXISTS dev_db;       # 💥 Nuke DB
```

